OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with scattered showers.
OL,6,FThese showers become frequent, heavy
OL,7,Fand blustery with hail and thunder at
OL,8,Ftimes from the morning. The strong
OL,9,Fsouth to southwest wind will reach
OL,10,Fgale force in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBlustery showers will clear
OL,13,Fback to the northwest during the
OL,14,Fevening. Increasing clear periods and
OL,15,Fwinds falling light bring a patchy
OL,16,Finland frost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FThe morning will be mostly dry
OL,19,Fwith bright spells. Cloud and
OL,20,Fscattered showers spread northeast
OL,21,Fduring the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
