OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods Tuesday. Cloud and
OL,7,Frain, heavy at times, spreads
OL,8,Fnortheast late Tuesday and continues
OL,9,Fthrough Wednesday. The rain turns
OL,10,Fshowery during Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
